data.rationale:
I selected this namespace because this is a drop-in replacement for
    a module I wrote earlier (Games::Go::SGF2misc::GD) which I had
    Jettero bundle into Games::Go::SGF2misc. I am applying for a new
    namespace so that users of Games::Go::SGF2misc can have an alternate
    (better) rendering backend available.
